     "Thrombospondins: multifunctional regulators of cell interactions."
     Annu. Rev. Cell Dev. Biol. 17:25-51(2001).
     PubMed=11687483; DOI=10.1146/annurev.cellbio.17.1.25
[ 2] Kvansakul M., Adams J.C., Hohenester E.
