     calcium core in the type 3 repeats."
     EMBO J. 23:1223-1233(2004).
     PubMed=15014436; DOI=10.1038/sj.emboj.7600166
[ 3] Carlson C.B., Bernstein D.A., Annis D.S., Misenheimer T.M.,
     Hannah B.L., Mosher D.F., Keck J.L.
     "Structure of the calcium-rich signature domain of human
